thread.title_full: OrderingOnlineSystem - OrderingCo - Ordering.co bewertet von Borima

author: Borima
title: Borima
text: I'm switching from my previous online food ordering system to OOS for its feature rich and dependable team for support and customization. Migration to new system is hard but OOS support help me along the way. There are bugs and they fixed them very fast. Almost done setting up new system and migration... can't wait to go live!
